:1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"我自己就連個盤 用水浸滿個盤 之後倒左d 水<br />\n咁就有少少水留向燒賣度<br />\n再拎去叮"},{"pid":"b253c303bd14fbf2675b66f21ae329dfcb014c75","tid":1950922,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T18:00:47.000Z","msg":"ching脾老婆打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"823d79b52478e6fb2564e83e506a5df03f23158e","tid":1950922,"uid":59678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b253c303bd14fbf2675b66f21ae329dfcb014c75","tid":1950922,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T18:00:47.000Z","msg":"ching脾老婆打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:16:32.000Z","msg":"亂用佢啲煲煲鍋鍋就會俾佢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係用微波爐叮嘢算"},{"pid":"f066ac8c42353cc48ad8ea740bf3125590c5fe3c","tid":1950922,"uid":117344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:19:40.000Z","msg":"吓燒賣就咁就食得啦先乜叮"},{"pid":"12017086836a5a7138104108ef1d95f2792bd7d1","tid":1950922,"uid":59678,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1edeb61778a10293e08f18e6aecdf14584b7afb1","tid":1950922,"uid":33077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"我自己就連個盤 用水浸滿個盤 之後倒左d 水<br />\n咁就有少少水留向燒賣度<br />\n再拎去叮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:33:59.000Z","msg":"用密實盒叮燒賣二次。<br />\n第一次：<br />\n平鋪排列燒賣，加水至與黃色皮水平，以800W 1分30秒加熱。<br />\n加熱後倒去多餘水份。<br />\n第二次：<br />\n加入少許昆布冷麵汁代替豉油，以800W 1分鐘加熱。<br />\n進食前加入少許麻油辣油，完成。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOM5Tkp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOM5Tkp.png&h=728a10c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n食落好似老婆啲肉咁彈咁有口感<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}